---
title: Sweet Paprika Chicken & Rice with Creamy Parsley Sauce
description: Mild, sweet paprika not only turns this creamy sauce a gorgeous shade of red, but it also adds an unmistakable layer of flavour to this chicken dinner. Plain rice is all you need to mop up the addictive sauce, with a few colourful veggies thrown in for an extra hearty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cc9168cc77d57000a4eed99-199db769.jpg
